    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay cool. i've got the data ready. basically we ran some tests on a group of 10 participants to see how they interact with LLMs for reasoning tasks. can you take that info and turn it into a really strong, professional abstract that doesn't sound like a small pilot study?",
